Ignore local run progress files and logs
ingest_progress.json
*.log
build_log.txt
check_db.log
Ignore local Python runtime caching
pycache/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
venv/
.env
Ignore environment/IDE configurations
.vscode/
.DS_Store
